    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to proof increasing patient satisfaction and preservation of
      quality of life in patients with Gaucher's Disease receiving their enzyme replacement therapy
      with VPRIV (Velaglucerase alfa)at their home setting compared to receiving the infusions at
      the clinic or at doctor's practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
